{
  "stem": "16571.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 298.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for some reason or other, I always finish up going to the library, bringing back more books.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My wife used to say, leave them alone, leave them alone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't-- And I said, yeah, OK, OK, OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But every time, I come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I learned a lot from what was going on under my own nose, in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a book I read two or three times called It was written by the leader of the resistance in Paris.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what-- I mean, I was at Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he-- What I read, what he went through, and what happened to him, my hair stood up on end, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, as I said, I didn't know what was going on, what was happening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by reading books, I sort of educated myself, and as I said, I never had a lesson in my life.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And slowly, I finished up-- sort of, they asked you, what job-- jobs do you want to?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a half an address from America, because I had my aunt-- my father's brother-- my father's sister there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they decided that he was a jeweler, so they decided I should go to [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Garden, ?] learn to become a jeweler, which I was more than happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't until many years later, I think it was some-- somewhere in the-- in '61, '62, I went to America for the first time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was 40-- 55-pound return.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I met up with my cousins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My auntie had died by then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I'm telling-- you see?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My auntie-- I've got a photo of my auntie with me on-- by her big, long car.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
